sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant APW as «view»<br>:AdminProfileWindow
    participant APC as «controller»<br>:AdminProfileController
    participant A as Admin

    note over Admin,A: USE CASE 1: VIEW ACCOUNT (ADMIN)
    Admin->>+APW: request to view profile
    APW->>+APC: index()
    APC->>+A: get admin details
    A-->>-APC: return admin data
    APC-->>-APW: return profile view with data
    APW-->>-Admin: display admin profile

    note over Admin,A: USE CASE 2: EDIT ACCOUNT (ADMIN)
    Admin->>+APW: modify profile details & submit
    APW->>+APC: update(request)
    APC->>+A: update admin record
    A-->>-APC: update confirmed
    APC-->>-APW: return redirect
    APW-->>-Admin: display updated profile

    note over Admin,A: USE CASE 3: UPDATE PASSWORD (ADMIN)
    Admin->>+APW: submit new password
    APW->>+APC: updatePassword(request)
    APC->>+A: update password field
    A-->>-APC: password updated
    APC-->>-APW: return redirect
    APW-->>-Admin: display success message
